{
  "stem": "3277.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But he was luckier than me, because he was a specialist in that, uh-- cooling, in the refrigeration.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he-- finally, he got a job at the border in Poland, where they-- the fishing, where they froze those-- those fish.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he said, I will try to get some connections and get from over there to Stockholm, to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he used to-- came back to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He said, Mark, listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "At that time, I was Majer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Listen-- no chance.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Then he went back, but still was trying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And in the meantime, you know, I got a vacation, and I went to the mountains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "When I came back, I-- somebody told me that he-- you see, over there, where he was, you couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You needed special permission.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he called to the-- where I used to live in Waldenburg to get the permission and to come to-- to his place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when I came back, it was too late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was already in Sweden-- illegally, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But how this happened-- he got a Polack who was, you know, working in the post office and putting-- mail into the cars to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he couldn't put him as the mail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Polish government used to export salt to Sweden.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got an-- made an arrangement that he got some-- a lot of those blankets, and he put him into such-- car with salt.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was shipped in a carton of salt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And shipped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, he was shipped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you can find out-- you can find out how I was feeling, that he was in Stockholm and I was here then.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he was so nice to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to write letters.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
